(95, 8, 15, 'Lancio del dado', '1629700771_1629488397_img_c.webp', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PROBLEMA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Carica in un array i punti ottenuti lanciando un dado a 6 facce. Sono previsti dieci lanci. Visualizzare l&amp;#39;array dopo i dieci lanci.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DIAGRAMMA A BLOCCHI&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Clicca qui per visualizzare il&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/579636638.svg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Diagramma a blocchi&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CODICE SORGENTE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;#include &amp;lt;stdio.h&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n#include &amp;lt;stdlib.h&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n#include &amp;lt;time.h&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n//dichiarazione costante&lt;br /&gt;\r\n#define NUMERO_DADI 3&lt;br /&gt;\r\n//dichiarazione funzioni&lt;br /&gt;\r\nvoid menu();&lt;br /&gt;\r\nvoid play();&lt;br /&gt;\r\nvoid lancio_dadi();&lt;br /&gt;\r\nvoid generazione_dadi();&lt;br /&gt;\r\nvoid risultati();&lt;br /&gt;\r\nvoid informazioni();&lt;br /&gt;\r\nvoid contatti();&lt;br /&gt;\r\nvoid esci();&lt;br /&gt;\r\nvoid banner_time();&lt;br /&gt;\r\nvoid banner_grazie();&lt;br /&gt;\r\nint main(int argc, char *argv[]){&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;//sezione dichiarativa&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;int c;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;int dadi[NUMERO_DADI];&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;//sezione menu&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;do {&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;menu();&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; c=getch();&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; switch (c) {&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;case &amp;#39;1&amp;#39;:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; play(dadi);&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; break;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;case &amp;#39;2&amp;#39;:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; informazioni();&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; break;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;case &amp;#39;3&amp;#39;:&l