(138, 8, 17, 'Ridimensionamento celle', '1629983767_1629973100_1629712667_16294883297_img_c.webp', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Per ridimensionare le celle ci sono vari metodi.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIl primo metodo &amp;egrave; cliccare con il tasto destro sulla lettera per modificare la misura della colonna altrimenti sul numero per modificare la riga. &amp;egrave; possibile selezionare anche pi&amp;ugrave; celle o pi&amp;ugrave; colonne.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/477074157.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Fatto ci&amp;ograve; comparir&amp;agrave; un piccolo menu dove baster&amp;agrave; selezionare la voce altezza riga o colonna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/2035399874.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Per modificare invece le celle con un&amp;rsquo;unit&amp;agrave; di misura baster&amp;agrave; recarsi nella scheda visualizza&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/2004642313.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;e nella sezione visualizzazione cartella di lavoro&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1880372441.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&g