(139, 8, 17, 'Inserire un\'immagine', '1629986469_1629973100_1629712667_16294883297_img_c.webp', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Per prima cosa selezionare la scheda inserisci,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1577938671.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;recarsi nella sezione illustrazioni&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/945374248.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;e qui cliccare su immagini,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/2064001787.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;si aprir&amp;agrave; un menu a tendina sul quali saranno presenti due voci. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1054902112.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Selezionando la prima avremo la possibilit&amp;agrave; di scegliere un&amp;rsquo;immagine presente sul nostro dispositivo, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/160204091.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt