(140, 8, 17, 'Creare macro in maniera veloce e assegnarla ad un\'immagine', '1629988982_1629973100_1629712667_16294883297_img_c.webp', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Recarsi nella scheda sviluppo&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1855469268.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;tengo a precisare che la scheda sviluppo non viene visualizzata per impostazione predefinita, ma &amp;egrave; possibile aggiungerla alla barra multifunzione. Nella scheda file scegliere Opzioni&amp;gt; personalizzare la barra multifunzione. In Personalizzazione della barra multifunzione e Schede principali selezionare la casella di controllo Sviluppo. Fatta questa promessa ritorniamo nella scheda sviluppo, dove baster&amp;agrave; cliccare su &amp;ldquo;registra macro&amp;rdquo; presente nella sezione codice.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/494566870.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Sulla finestra che vi si apre, assegnare un nome.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1644996496.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Avviata la registrazione baster&amp;agrave; eseguire le azioni che vogliamo che assimili la macro. Fatto ci&amp;ograve; baster&amp;agrave; interrompere la registrazione della macro.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1935233998.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Una volta eseguiti questi passaggi per assegnarla ad un&amp;rsquo;immagine baster&amp;agrave; cliccare con il tasto destro su l&amp;rsquo;elemento,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/2083643513.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;e sul menu che vi appare cliccare sulla voce &amp;ldquo;assegna macro&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/228825178.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Nella finestra selezionare la macro da noi creata&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/606686203.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;e premere su OK.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1264419174.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;La nostra macro &amp;egrave; stata assegnata all&amp;rsquo;immagine.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, '2021-08-26 16:43:02'),
(141, 8, 17, 'Formattare celle in base al loro valore', '1629990370_1629973100_1629712667_16294883297_img_c.webp', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Recarsi nella scheda home,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/867608077.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;nella sezione stili&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/96407382.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;cliccare su &amp;ldquo;formattazione condizionale&amp;rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/325301400.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;qui si aprir&amp;agrave; un menu a tendina&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/687570669.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;dove baster&amp;agrave; cliccare sulla voce &amp;ldquo;crea nuova regola&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1525434891.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quo