idth:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Dopo recarsi nella parte sottostante e applicare una formattazione alla cella che conterr&amp;agrave; quel range di valori.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/102630524.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Creata la regola ora bisogna assegnarla, basta riandare nella sezione stili, cliccare su formattazione condizionale e cliccare su &amp;ldquo;gestisci regole&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/2006943244.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Nella finestra che appare baster&amp;agrave; selezionare la casella &amp;ldquo;si applica a&amp;rdquo; e individuare nel foglio l&amp;rsquo;intervallo di celle desiderato.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/141556548.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Dopo di che cliccare OK.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1650210102.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, '2021-08-26 17:06:10'),
