(143, 8, 17, 'Funzione STRINGA.ESTRAI', '1630059138_162997310099.webp', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;funzione stringa.estrai &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Selezionare una cella &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/779271943.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;e a sinistra della barra della formula &amp;egrave; presente fx, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1869574556.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;basta premerlo e si aprir&amp;agrave; una finestra con tutte una serie di funzioni noi andremo a vedere nello specifico la funzione stringa.estrai. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/81024839.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Selezioniamo e clicchiamo su ok, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1847839855.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;qui si aprir&amp;agrave; una nuova finestra dove compariranno tre campi: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;..