(144, 8, 17, 'Nascondere elementi del foglio', '1630059918_162997310099.webp', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Come nascondere la grigia di righe e colonne, andare nella scheda visualizza&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1046672261.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;e nella sezione mostra&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1599155584.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;togliere la punta alla casella griglia,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/1751346576.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;la griglia verr&amp;agrave; tolta soltanto al foglio attuale. Per rivedere la griglia baster&amp;agrave; mettere la spunta nella casella. Come nascondere le intestazioni delle righe e colonne, andare nella scheda visualizza&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/71800442.webp&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;e nella sezione mostra&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/posts/body/757831889.webp&quot; style=&quot;w